OL,6,FHe failed three times to attend an
OL,7,Fenquiry about the matter at his local
OL,8,FParish Hall and was eventually fined
OL,9,F#575 after pleading guilty at Jersey
OL,10,FMagistrate's Court.
OL,12,FDelivering a personal statement in the
OL,13,FStates Chamber on Monday (8 September)
OL,14,Fahead of the vote, Deputy Ozouf
OL,15,Foffered "a full and unreserved
OL,16,Fapology" for what happened and added,
OL,17,F"This experience has been profoundly
OL,18,Fhumbling and distressing".
