OL,6,FHe referenced his recent ADHD
OL,7,Fdiagnosis and said it is "not an
OL,8,Fexcuse. However, it offers an
OL,9,Fexplanation as to why I have found
OL,10,Fcertain issues so challenging".
OL,12,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Deputy Ozouf
OL,13,Fadded: "I am sorry on that one
OL,14,Foccasion I was speeding, it was a
OL,15,Flapse of judgment.
