OL,6,FHowever, speaking to ITV News, Deputy
OL,7,FSteve Ahier from the PPC Committee
OL,8,Fsaid: "The fact that the Deputy failed
OL,9,Fto turn up for three Parish Hall
OL,10,FEnquiries and then only turned up to
OL,11,Fthe Magistrate's Court because he was
OL,12,Fadvised by a member of the public,
OL,13,Fit's the lack of engagement. The total
OL,14,Fdisrespect for procedure is the big
OL,15,Fproblem."
OL,17,FA full list of the States Members who
OL,18,Fvoted for and against Deputy Ozouf's
OL,19,Fsuspension can be found here on the
OL,20,FAssembly's website.
